        "timestamp": "2018-02-08 17:49:41.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nSoftHSM is from its original repo, there is a note in README to makr the commit id for our baseline code.\nAs to mirror, it is tricky, so far I have no plan to put it on github.\nif we put modified SoftHSMv2 on github, we can use git submodules to pull from there, but time is tight, we have to copy the codes and modify it, this is most simple way to us.",
